Package com.flexganttfx.model.dateline Description

Classes used to support the dateline (child control of timeline). The dateline model defines the various resolutions that are available for the dateline when zooming in or out. The model also specifies how many dateline scales (rows) are used by the dateline (1 to 5).
Since:
1.0
